Its not really what a Paladin would call a ship. Some old pieces of wood nailed to something that swims. <br>
Taino takes Febreezas hand and guides her on the ship, letting her get aboard first. Not that a warrioress would need this "help" but thats the little gestures that are asked and appropriate from a Paladin. <br>
<br>
